abstract: Democrats in the U.S. House of Representatives unveiled formal charges against Donald Trump on Tuesday, moving quickly toward a momentous vote on whether to impeach the Republican president.
snippet: Democrats in the U.S. House of Representatives unveiled formal charges against Donald Trump on Tuesday, moving quickly toward a momentous vote on whether to impeach the Republican president.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - Democrats in the U.S. House of Representatives unveiled formal charges against Donald Trump on Tuesday, moving quickly toward a momentous vote on whether to impeach the Republican president.
headline_main: Factbox: Democrats Announce Impeachment Charges Against Trump
headline_print_headline: Factbox: Democrats Announce Impeachment Charges Against Trump

abstract: Democrats in the U.S. House of Representatives introduced two articles of impeachment against President Donald Trump, charging him with abuse of power and obstruction of Congress.
snippet: Democrats in the U.S. House of Representatives introduced two articles of impeachment against President Donald Trump, charging him with abuse of power and obstruction of Congress.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Democrats in the U.S. House of Representatives introduced two articles of impeachment against President Donald Trump, charging him with abuse of power and obstruction of Congress.
headline_main: U.S. Democrats Introduce Two Articles of Impeachment Against Trump
headline_print_headline: U.S. Democrats Introduce Two Articles of Impeachment Against Trump

abstract: There is a dawning realization among voters that the prime minister’s vow to complete Brexit could undermine the N.H.S.
snippet: There is a dawning realization among voters that the prime minister’s vow to complete Brexit could undermine the N.H.S.
lead_paragraph: COVENTRY, England — Along with millions of Britons, Jules Barcroft bought into the bold promise made by Boris Johnson in the 2016 Brexit campaign: that leaving the European Union would bring buckets of new money into the long starved National Health Service.

abstract: Democratic leaders unveiled articles of impeachment charging President Trump with abuse of power and obstruction of Congress.
snippet: Democratic leaders unveiled articles of impeachment charging President Trump with abuse of power and obstruction of Congress.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — House Democratic leaders on Tuesday formally called for President Trump’s removal from office, asserting that he “ignored and injured the interests of the nation” in two articles of impeachment that charged him with abusing his power and obstructing Congress.

abstract: The Taliban abducted as many as 45 elderly family members of a late Afghan government employee who were attending his funeral, officials said Tuesday.
snippet: The Taliban abducted as many as 45 elderly family members of a late Afghan government employee who were attending his funeral, officials said Tuesday.
lead_paragraph: KABUL, Afghanistan — The Taliban abducted as many as 45 elderly family members of a late Afghan government employee who were attending his funeral, officials said Tuesday.
headline_main: Taliban Abduct 45 People From Gov't Employee's Funeral
headline_print_headline: Taliban Abduct 45 People From Gov't Employee's Funeral

abstract: House Democrats and the White House announced a deal Tuesday on a modified North American trade pact, handing President Donald Trump a major Capitol Hill win on the same day that impeachment charges were announced against him. Both sides hailed the deal as a win for American workers.
snippet: House Democrats and the White House announced a deal Tuesday on a modified North American trade pact, handing President Donald Trump a major Capitol Hill win on the same day that impeachment charges were announced against him. Both sides hailed th...
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — House Democrats and the White House announced a deal Tuesday on a modified North American trade pact, handing President Donald Trump a major Capitol Hill win on the same day that impeachment charges were announced against him. Both sides hailed the deal as a win for American workers.
headline_main: Democrats, White House Forge New North American Trade Deal
headline_print_headline: Democrats, White House Forge New North American Trade Deal

abstract: The president suggested he lacked confidence in his own F.B.I. director, who did not share his negative view of a long-awaited inspector general report.
snippet: The president suggested he lacked confidence in his own F.B.I. director, who did not share his negative view of a long-awaited inspector general report.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — President Trump and Attorney General William P. Barr took aim at the F.B.I. on Tuesday, escalating their attacks on the bureau a day after an independent watchdog concluded that former F.B.I. officials had adequate reason in 2016 to open the investigation into the Trump campaign’s ties to Russia.

abstract: U.S. productivity fell in the summer, the first decline in nearly four years, underscoring the struggles companies are facing in boosting worker efficiency.

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — U.S. productivity fell in the summer, the first decline in nearly four years, underscoring the struggles companies are facing in boosting worker efficiency.
